<h2>OVIRT</h2>
<p>The growth of an open virtualization ecosystem requires more than just the hypervisor. That's why we joined industry leaders in creating oVirt. This project has been seeded with assets from Red Hat by open sourcing its virtualization management software, Red Hat Enterprise Virtualization.</p>

<p class="look"><a href="http://www.ovirt.org">Read more about oVirt</a></p>

<h2>Open Virtualization Alliance</h2>
<p>Comprised of leading virtualization, datacenter, and cloud solution providers, the OVA's mission is to foster adoption of open source virtualization technologies, and drive innovation and interoperability within the enterprise software market for open virtualization solutions. The OVA is an important advocate for organizations who want a true open source and interoperable virtualization solution.</p>

<p class="look"><a href="http://www.openvirtualizationalliance.org/">Read more about OVA</a></p>

